import { Box, Button, Checkbox, Stack } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import React from 'react'

const Content = () => {
  return (
    <Stack spacing={5}
            bg="white" mt="10px"
        >
            <Box>
                <Checkbox size='lg' colorScheme='orange' defaultChecked ml="5px">
                    Checkbox
                </Checkbox>
            </Box>
            <Box>
                <Checkbox size='lg' colorScheme='orange' defaultChecked ml="5px">
                    Checkbox
                </Checkbox>
                <Button>X</Button>
            </Box>
        </Stack>
  )
}

export default Content
